<p>Let's say I have a route:</p>  <pre class="lang-php prettyprint-override"><code>Route::get('.../{abc}/...', [   'uses' =&gt; 'API\SomeApiController@progress' ]); </code></pre>  <p>The <code>SomeApiController::progress()</code> method gets the object <code>ApiRequest</code> as an argument:</p>  <pre class="lang-php prettyprint-override"><code>public function progress(ApiRequest $request, $abc) </code></pre>  <p>How can I get the value of <code>abc</code> in the <code>ApiRequest::authorize()</code> method?</p>